       array('Type'=>'Hours','Number_Of_Stats'=>12, 'Description'=>'Hours Tapestries have 12 Stats, these are amongst the most complicated that most Yarn-tellers will want to use. There is a great deal of variety in Stats created by Hours Tapestries, depeding upon the genre and setting.','Facet_Distribution'=>'12 Stats of 2 Facets each.'),
       array('Type'=>'Malefic','Number_Of_Stats'=>13, 'Description'=>'Malefic Tapestries have 13 Stats, they are the most complicated Stats that Tapestries usually create. ','Facet_Distribution'=>'13 Stats, 11 of 2 Facets and 2 of 1 Facet each.'),
